---
title: Teriyaki Glazed Chicken with Garlic Rice & Soy Veggies
description: The sweet and savoury elements of this easy teriyaki chicken make a speedy meal that doesn't skimp on flavour! With aromatic garlic rice and a colourful veggie stir-fry, it's a family favourite that's sure to satisfy.
